    "While CALM2 and llm-jp are pretrained from scratch to construct a Japanese LLM, Swallow is a Japanese continual pre-training model of Llama 2 (Table 2) (Touvron et al., 2023; Fujii et al., 2024; Sugimoto, 2024).",
    "We train the SFT models using Direct Preference Optimization (DPO) (Rafailov et al., 2023) with a Low-Rank Adaptation (LoRA) (Hu et al., 2022; Sidahmed et al., 2024).",
    "We label the correct answer as the chosen response and the wrong answer as the rejected response.",
    "For the SFT model, we evaluate the 3-shot learning performance with the examples from the development set.",
